						<p class="text-gray-600">Technical and cultural fit assessment with thorough vetting.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mx-auto mb-4">4</div>
